  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p735539/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.hjfile.cn/doc/201506/33d6d0488c724acfbb4971f3a5967a54.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t【新词】</p>\n<p>\n\t<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/kitchen pass\" target=\"_blank\">kitchen pass</a></p>\n<p>\n\tn. Permission from one's spouse to attend an event or go on an outing.</p>\n<p>\n\tkitchen pass，不要被字面意思骗了。并不是指你进厨房还要得到允许，而是指如果你要出去的话，得先得到在厨房里忙活的伴侣的同意。</p>\n<p>\n\t不过这个短语和妻管严（hen-pecked husband）还是有区别的。妻管严还可以用：be tired to one's apron strings 来表达，被系到某人的围裙上，可想而知受控制的程度啦。</p>\n<p>\n\t【栗子】</p>\n<p>\n\tkitchen pass</p>\n<p>\n\t1. Kitchen pass refers to permission from one's spouse to attend an event or go on an outing.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">Kitchen pass指夫妻中的一方对另一方出席活动或者出游的许可。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t2. James plans to go out for hiking with some of his friends next week, but he has to get the kitchen pass from his wife.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">詹姆斯打算下周跟一些朋友去远足，但他必须先得到太太的允许。</span></p>\n<p>\n\then-pecked husband</p>\n<p>\n\tMax never comes out with the rest of us, for he's a hen-pecked husband.<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">麦克斯从不跟我们出去，因为他是妻管严。</span></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p735539/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p735539\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p735394/\">朋友圈热议人贩子死刑 在外国如何定罪？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p735062/\">时尚小窍门：8招改变生活的美丽秘诀</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p735315/\">一张图告诉你：2100年的地球将有多热？</